    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2261591/" class="title-link">名不副实</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2261591"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4402632/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4402632-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4402632/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">文盲</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-23"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-23 02:21:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2261591_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这书名大而无甚大用，范围基本不出郑注，孔疏。大略是一个《礼记正义》的简本，偶引他说，鲜有发明。唐人旧疏，《礼记》终清一代，无人新疏，无以加也！无以加也！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2261591/#comments">(11回应)</a>
